    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/3f58c07032e29b7cf5de4b32a84b3cb2.avif?t=1752209873\" width=616 height=48 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/bb62c7ee9680fb02a6f75ea6e777d4c3.webp?t=1752209873\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/bb62c7ee9680fb02a6f75ea6e777d4c3.poster.avif?t=1752209873\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=240 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用卡牌放置或强化建筑、施展魔法，自由构筑专属卡组，打造独特的防御策略。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/c78650aa87e1c185059137c29157e799.avif?t=1752209873\" width=616 height=48 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/c017e8d8efadf76df098568863301f34.webp?t=1752209873\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/c017e8d8efadf76df098568863301f34.poster.avif?t=1752209873\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=240 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降临，黑暗大军蜂拥而至，你的部队和防御塔将自主进攻敌人，守护女神像。兵种组合和强化效果的选择将成为制胜关键。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/00479156470266670e36ba57e74a1895.avif?t=1752209873\" width=616 height=48 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/402763388de0839ce4cc05c7540a38ce.webp?t=1752209873\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/402763388de0839ce4cc05c7540a38ce.poster.avif?t=1752209873\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=240 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位女神都会带来不同的初始遗物和卡组体系，并随着成长解锁更多强化。每次击退敌人，你都可以获得不同的卡牌、遗物作为奖励，或遭遇随机事件让命运走向未知的方向。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/46b5a5375b9f856b8eada2a878b4c8f7.avif?t=1752209873\" width=616 height=48 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/e1f9e8a3640f455529ed7d38f6fded49.webp?t=1752209873\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183220/extras/e1f9e8a3640f455529ed7d38f6fded49.poster.avif?t=1752209873\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=240 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由搭配不同的卡牌、遗物和建筑强化，构筑强大的的防线守护女神，抵抗黑暗的入侵！</p>",
